interaction (F(1, 204) = 7.70, p = 0.006).

[HYPOTHESES]
products predominantly associated with utilitarian attitudes at the product category level support less utilitarian and more symbolic attitudes at the brand level, while products predominantly associated with symbolic attitudes at the product category level support less symbolic and more utilitarian attitudes at the brand level 
